{
  "chapter": 39,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十回预谋在先。本章围绕谢晓峰与六派高手的赌剑对决展开。吴涛负气离去后，谢晓峰以偷天换日夺剑式轻松击败梅长华，又以轻妙剑法化解欧阳云鹤的飞龙九式。厉真真揭示她与六人分别打赌：若六人皆败于谢晓峰三招之内，她虽输给谢晓峰却赢了六人，可借此推动七派联盟推举她为盟主。黎平子欲泄露秘密，却被欧阳云鹤一肘击碎肋骨后刺杀。田在龙愤而欲走，被梅长华和秦独秀联手刺死。厉真真揭露田在龙是天尊奸细，并指向简传学为证据——暗示简传学出卖了谢晓峰的行踪与伤情。本章展现了七派联盟背后的政治阴谋与背叛。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_tao",
      "speaker_name": "吴涛",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "你放心，我们的约会，我绝不会忘记。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_wu_tao",
      "text": "我相信。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，胜就是胜，败就是败，点苍门下，果然是君子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黎平子",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "幸好我不是君子。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "text": "不是君子有什么好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黎平子",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "就因为我不是君子，所以绝不会抢着出手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "text": "你的确不是君子，你是个小人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_chang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "梅长华",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那么最吃亏的就是我这种人了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mei_chang_hua",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_chang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "梅长华",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我既不是君子，也不是小人，虽不愿争先，也不愿落后。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mei_chang_hua",
      "text": "你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "果然是天下无双的剑法。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只可惜出手并不正，以谢家三少爷的身份，本不该如此取巧的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "他受了伤，在你们七位高手的环伺之下，当然要速战速决，出奇制胜！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "你也懂得剑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "我不懂剑，这道理我却懂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "有理，说得有理，谢家的三少爷，本来就绝对不能败的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "他若不败，你就要败了，你高兴什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "你不懂？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "我不懂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "想不到世上居然还有你不懂的事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黎平子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我告诉你！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "text": "你们说过的话，算数不算数？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黎平子",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "我们说过什么话？我早就忘了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "text": "我没有忘。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "text": "幸好你是个守约守信的君子。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黎平子",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "text": "他是君子，他要守约守信，是他的事，我只不过是个小人，小人说出来的话都可以当做放屁。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "text": "放屁也是人生大事之一，我保证绝没有人会拦住你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黎平子",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那就好极了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "text": "我想得到。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黎平子",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "但你绝对想不到，她跟我们每个人也都打了个赌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "text": "赌什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黎平子",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "她赌我们六个人全都接不住你的三招。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "text": "所以她若输给了我，就反而赢了你们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黎平子",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "她只输给你一个人，却赢了我们六个人，她赢的远比输的多得多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实你们早就知道，吃亏的事，我是绝不会做的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "text": "她跟你们赌的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黎平子",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你知不知道天尊？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黎平子",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "近来天尊的势力日益庞大，七大剑派已不能坐视，老一辈的人多已闭关不出，我们这一代的弟子，就决定要在泰山聚会，组成七派联盟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "text": "这是个好主意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黎平子",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "在那一天，我们当然还得推出一位主盟的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "text": "你们若是输给了她，就得要推她为盟主？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黎平子",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "一点也不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "text": "就算你们推我做了盟主，又有什么不好！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黎平子",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "只有一点不好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "text": "哪一点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黎平子",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "你太聪明了，我们若是推你做了盟主，这泰山之盟，只怕就要变成第二个天尊。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "text": "现在昆仑、华山、崆峒、点苍，都已在片刻之间，惨败在三少爷的剑下，你难道有把握能接得住他三招？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黎平子",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "我没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "text": "其实我也早就知道你是个言而无信的小人，幸好别人都不是的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "我也是的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "text": "你？你也像他一样？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "我不能不这么做，江湖中已不能再出现第二个天尊。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黎平子",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "text": "现在你虽然已不能算是真正的君子，却是个真正的男子汉了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": "char_li_ping_zi",
      "text": "也许我本来就不是君子。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我欧阳云鹤平生最恨的，就是这种言而无信的小人，只恨不得要他们一个个全都死在我的剑下，各位若认为我杀错了，我也不妨以死谢罪。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "text": "他们都知道你的为人，绝不会这么想的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "胜就是胜，败就是败，各位都是君子，当然绝不会食言背信。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_zai_long",
      "speaker_name": "田在龙",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "text": "我不是君子，现在我只要一听到这个字，就觉得说不出的恶心。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": "char_tian_zai_long",
      "text": "那么田师兄的意思是——",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_zai_long",
      "speaker_name": "田在龙",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "text": "我没有什么意思，只不过泰山我已不想去了，你们随便要推什么人做盟主，都已经跟我没关系。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_du_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "秦独秀",
      "listener": "char_tian_zai_long",
      "text": "你不去，我也不去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_chang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "梅长华",
      "listener": "char_tian_zai_long",
      "text": "我更不会去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_zai_long",
      "speaker_name": "田在龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我们一起走，有谁能拦得住我们！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_zai_long",
      "speaker_name": "田在龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_chang_hua",
      "text": "你们好狠！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_chang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "梅长华",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这是柄好剑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mei_chang_hua",
      "text": "是好剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_chang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "梅长华",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这柄剑在华山世代相传，已有三百年，从来没有落在外人手里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mei_chang_hua",
      "text": "我相信。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_chang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "梅长华",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你若认为我刚才不该杀了田在龙，不妨用这柄剑来杀了我，我死而无怨。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mei_chang_hua",
      "text": "他本就该死，我更该死，因为我们都看错了人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这么样的结果，本来就在我们计划之中。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "text": "你们当然也早已知道我是个快死了的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我们的确早已知道你最多只能再活三天。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "江湖中的消息，本就传得极快，何况是你的消息。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们当然也看得出，刚才我一出手，创口就已崩裂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我们就算看不出，也能想得到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你们都认为，像我这么样一个人，本不该再管别人的闲事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "但是我们还是同样尊敬你，不管你是生是死，都已保全了神剑山庄的威名。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "至少我们都已承认败了，是败在你手下的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道，这一点我也很感激，只可惜你们忘了一点。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "哪一点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "有我在这里，田在龙和黎平子本不该死的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为你觉得你应该可以救他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "所以你觉得你虽然没有杀他们，他们却无异因你而死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "所以你想替他们复仇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "也许并不是想为他们复仇，只不过是想求自己的心安。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我明白你的意思，你反正要死了，就算死在我们剑下，也死得心安理得，问心无愧。只可惜你还有很多事都不知道。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你只不过看见了这件事表面上的一层，就下了判断，内中的真相，你根本就不想知道，你连问都没有问。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "我应该问什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "至少你应该问问，黎平子和田在龙是不是也有该死的原因。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "他们该死？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "当然该死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "绝对该死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为他们不死，我们的七派联盟，根本就无法成立。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为他们不死，死的人就要更多了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "黎平子偏激任性，本就是成事不足，败事有余的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我们要成大事，就不能不将这种人牺牲。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我对他的死，还有点难受，可是田在龙……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "田在龙就算再死十次，也是罪有应得的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为他本来就是个奸细！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "奸细？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你不知道奸细是什么意思，奸细就是种会出卖人的人。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "他出卖了谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他出卖了我们，也出卖了自己。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "买主是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "是天尊。当然是天尊。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你应该想得到的，只有天尊，才有资格收买田在龙这种人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "你有证据？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你想看证据？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "text": "我想。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "证据就在这里。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "这个人就是证据。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你是谢家的三少爷，你是天下无双的剑客，你当然不会是个笨蛋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那么你自己为什么不想想，我们怎么会知道你最多只能活三天的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 391,
      "line_end": 391
    }
  ],
